  "title": "⭐ B2B Client Engagement Crew (Entry-Level / ORD Friendly)",
  "description": "<p>🎓 WANT A FUN FIRST JOB IN MARKETING? JUMP IN! <br>\nMeet clients, work on B2B campaigns &amp; learn the ropes hands-on.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Your Role:</strong><br>\n• Engage corporate clients face-to-face<br>\n•  Support B2B campaign rollouts<br>\n•  Help manage client queries &amp; follow-ups<br>\n•  Develop strong people &amp; persuasion skills</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Why You’ll Love It:</strong><br>\n•  Entry-level — open to fresh grads &amp; ORD<br>\n•  Supportive team atmosphere<br>\n•  Active, social &amp; non-deskbound role</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>💸 Weekly Pay + Attractive Bonuses<br>\n📈 Build B2B confidence fast<br>\n🔥 Real exposure to the business marketing world</p>",
